<DealerHubLayout title="Dealer Onboarding Checklist | Pinnacle Sales" activeSection="Onboarding">

<h1>Dealer Onboarding Checklist</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Welcome to the WW Wood dealer network! Follow this roadmap to ensure your launch goes smoothly.</p>

<h2>Step 1 — Place Initial Sample Order</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-1">✓</span><div><strong>Request your starter kit</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Email your Pinnacle Sales territory rep with your sample-order request for approval and processing. Your starter kit includes door samples and color chips at a 50% showroom discount. We also recommend the full chip set with a sample of every color in chip format (SE Deck Complete). Download the correct form from <a href="/dealer-hub/order-samples">Order Samples</a>.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 2 — Door Sample Order Entered</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-2">✓</span><div><strong>Review your acknowledgment</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">WW Wood Customer Service will enter your sample order. You'll receive an acknowledgment email — review your door-sample and color-chip order within 24 hours of receipt. Mark any corrections on the acknowledgment and resend to <a href="mailto:orders@wwinc.com">orders@wwinc.com</a>.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 3 — Dealer Portal Activation</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-3">✓</span><div><strong>Activate your WW Wood portal account</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">The dealer portal lets you place, track, and inquire about orders. You'll receive an activation email from our team once your dealer number is issued. Activate immediately upon receipt. See <a href="/dealer-hub/ordering">Ordering SOPs</a> for the full order workflow.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 4 — Onboarding Training Session 1 (In-Person)</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-4">✓</span><div><strong>Product & sales orientation (~90 min)</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your territory manager will schedule an in-person session at your showroom. Covers cabinet construction and SKUs, finish overview, quoting tips, and competitive positioning. Target: within 10 days of receiving your samples. Review materials ahead of time on the <a href="/dealer-hub/training-product-deep-dive">Product Deep-Dive</a> and <a href="/dealer-hub/training-competitive-positioning">Competitive Positioning</a> pages.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 5 — Onboarding Training Session 2 (Live 2020 Webinar)</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-5">✓</span><div><strong>Hands-on 2020 Design catalog walkthrough (~90 min)</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Live webinar covering WW Wood 2020 Design catalogs: catalog setup, spec rules, pricing, and order-form export. Our Dealer Success & 2020 Specialist will reach out to schedule. Target: 1 week after your in-person session. Browse tutorials and tips on the <a href="/dealer-hub/training-2020-prokitchen">2020 Software Training</a> page.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 6 — Placing Your First Orders</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-6">✓</span><div><strong>Submit your first order for review</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your first 3-4 projects require a pre-order review before being sent to the factory. Email your order to our Dealer Success Specialist for review — expect a 48-hour turnaround. After your first few projects, you're cleared to order independently with <a href="/dealer-hub/submit">design reviews</a> available as needed. Follow the step-by-step process on the <a href="/dealer-hub/ordering">Ordering SOPs</a> page.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Additional Setup</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-7">✓</span><div><strong>Showroom display plan</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Work with Pinnacle Sales to plan displays that match <a href="/dealer-hub/showroom">showroom standards</a>. Includes layout, signage, and sample positioning.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-8">✓</span><div><strong>Download marketing assets</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Access brand logos, lifestyle photography, social content, and brochure templates from the <a href="/dealer-hub/marketing">Marketing Kit</a>.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-9">✓</span><div><strong>Warranty & service orientation</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">How to handle claims, warranty forms, replacements, and parts. Shiloh/Eclipse: 10-year warranty. Aspect: 5-year warranty. See <a href="/dealer-hub/support">Support & Escalation</a>.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-10">✓</span><div><strong>Schedule 30-day check-in</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your Pinnacle Sales rep will schedule a follow-up to review your experience, address any issues, and plan ongoing training.</span></div></li>
</ul>

